#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><p>
#: en/xml-guide.xml:278
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"This is a paragraph.  <path>/etc/passwd</path> is a file.\n"
"<uri>http://forums.gentoo.org</uri> is my favorite web site.\n"
"Type <c>ls</c> if you feel like it.  I <e>really</e> want to go to sleep now.\n"
