#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><p>
#: en/xml-guide.xml:348
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Epigraphs are sometimes used at the beginning of chapters to illustrate what is\n"
"to follow. It is simply a paragraph with a <c>by</c> attribute that contains\n"
"the signature.\n"
