#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><p>
#: en/xml-guide.xml:1191
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Try to use <c>&lt;uri&gt;</c> with the <c>link</c> attribute as much as\n"
"possible. In other words, the <uri link=\"http://forums.gentoo.org\">Gentoo\n"
"Forums</uri> is preferred over <uri>http://forums.gentoo.org</uri>.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><p>
#: en/xml-guide.xml:1197
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"When you comment something inside a <c>&lt;pre&gt;</c> construct, use\n"
"<c>&lt;comment&gt;</c> and parentheses or the comment marker for the language\n"
"that is being used (<c>#</c> for bash scripts and many other things, <c>//</c>\n"
"for C code, etc.) Also place the comment <e>before</e> the subject of the\n"
"comment.\n"
msgstr ""

